Completed Ralph slice `005C2-application-object-access-hardening`.

Implemented object-level access for loan application detail, patch, submit, and reference generation. Same-permission unrelated users now get `403 OBJECT_ACCESS_DENIED`; missing global permissions still return `403 PERMISSION_DENIED`; unknown applications still return `404 NOT_FOUND`. The implementation reuses the existing object-access helper via `applications.services.evaluate_application_object_access(...)`, with created/received users as owner facts and a narrow `credit_manager` override only in `credit_assessment`.

